\section{Tight-binding model}
\label{sec:tight_binding}

Here, we present a detailed derivation of the tight-binding model of the staggered square lattice PTI, leading to Eqs.~(1)--(2) of the main text.  Consider a generic two-waveguide coupler, which is described by the coupled mode Hamiltonian~\cite{supp_modulated_lattices},

